data.title: The Global Professional Tennis Coach Association (GPTCA)
data.meta_description: (GPTCA) is an international organization dedicated to educating, training, and assisting professional tennis coaches who wish to evolve at the ATP World Tour.
data.text:
2017-to-date

Serbia's Davis Cup team captain

Playing Career

Career High ATP ranking in doubles #1

Career High ATP ranking in singles #176

Recorded victories in singles over Andre Agassi, Nicolas Kiefer, Ivo Karlovic, Nicolas Mahut

Won 54 titles in doubles

Grand Slam titles / Doubles:

2010 Roland Garros doubles champion (w/ Daniel Nestor)

2008 and 2009 Wimbledon doubles champion (w/ Daniel Nestor)

2008 Tennis Masters Cup and 2010 ATP Finals doubles champion (w/ Daniel Nestor)

Grand Slam titles / Mixed doubles:

2014 Wimbledon champion (w/ Samantha Stosur)

2006 and 2010 Roland Garros champion (w/ Katarina Srebotnik)

2004 and 2008 Australian Open champion (w/ Elena Bovina , Sun Tiantian)

2013

Honoured with Davis Cup Award of Excellence

2010

Davis Cup champion with Serbia

Member of Serbia Davis Cup team (previously Yugoslavia / Serbia and Montenegro)
